WEBVTT

00:00:37.300 --> 00:00:40.580
=Reincarnated Love=

00:00:40.780 --> 00:00:43.700
=Episode 9=

00:00:43.700 --> 00:00:45.780
(Huo Mansion)

00:00:46.920 --> 00:00:47.760
Lady Wanyue,

00:00:47.880 --> 00:00:48.960
please wait.

00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:50.790
I've sent word to Mrs. Huo.

00:00:51.840 --> 00:00:52.920
Isn't this Lady Wanyue?

00:00:53.470 --> 00:00:54.310
What brings you here?

00:00:54.710 --> 00:00:55.550
Indeed.

00:01:00.960 --> 00:01:02.000
Ruoli knew I was here,

00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:03.140
yet she left me waiting here.

00:01:03.350 --> 00:01:04.190
What does she mean?

00:01:04.350 --> 00:01:05.430
Mrs. Huo is busy.

00:01:05.870 --> 00:01:07.680
Not everyone can meet her.

00:01:08.280 --> 00:01:09.120
Lady Wanyue,

00:01:09.430 --> 00:01:11.510
you just caused her to lose her child,

00:01:12.040 --> 00:01:13.280
and now you've come.

00:01:13.560 --> 00:01:15.230
The fact that she's willing to see you

00:01:15.433 --> 00:01:16.526
is already generous of her.

00:01:16.700 --> 00:01:17.560
Please stay patient

00:01:17.590 --> 00:01:18.710
and wait a little longer.

00:01:20.040 --> 00:01:20.880
You...

00:02:13.470 --> 00:02:14.430
Are you hurt?

00:02:15.840 --> 00:02:16.840
It's nothing.

00:02:16.910 --> 00:02:18.000
Thank you for your concern.

00:02:18.710 --> 00:02:20.400
Sorry, I deserve punishment.

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:21.960
You may leave.

00:02:22.310 --> 00:02:23.150
Yes.

00:02:25.910 --> 00:02:27.190
May I ask who you are?

00:02:29.560 --> 00:02:31.140
My name is Jiang Wanyue.

00:02:31.151 --> 00:02:32.740
I'm the second lady of the Jiang family.

00:02:32.840 --> 00:02:34.400
I've come to visit Cousin Ruoli.

00:02:36.080 --> 00:02:37.680
I am the eldest son of the Huo family,

00:02:37.800 --> 00:02:38.640
Lu Huaijin.

00:02:41.190 --> 00:02:44.080
You are both graceful and kind.

00:02:44.630 --> 00:02:46.750
Your sisterly bond is admirable.

00:02:47.750 --> 00:02:49.030
Thank you for your kind words.

00:02:49.520 --> 00:02:51.800
You have a noble and composed bearing.

00:02:52.190 --> 00:02:53.680
You truly have the bearing of an heir.

00:02:56.800 --> 00:02:58.280
Sorry for speaking out of turn.

00:02:58.630 --> 00:02:59.470
It's fine.

00:02:59.800 --> 00:03:00.640
You indeed

00:03:00.870 --> 00:03:01.710
understand me.

00:03:05.840 --> 00:03:08.190
Isn't there a man

00:03:08.470 --> 00:03:09.580
named Lu Huaijin?

00:03:10.560 --> 00:03:12.000
Go and get close to him.

00:03:12.560 --> 00:03:13.400
Win his favor.

00:03:15.150 --> 00:03:16.360
(I never expected Mr. Lu)

00:03:17.120 --> 00:03:18.280
(to be so fond of me.)

00:03:30.150 --> 00:03:30.990
Ruoli.

00:03:37.280 --> 00:03:38.120
Ruoli.

00:03:40.560 --> 00:03:41.766
Huaijin, what brings you here?

00:03:42.560 --> 00:03:43.590
You've lost your appetite

00:03:43.630 --> 00:03:44.470
because of Ruyan.

00:03:44.590 --> 00:03:46.590
I had some Jade Shrimp Dumplings made,

00:03:47.470 --> 00:03:48.310
but Yanzhi ate

00:03:48.590 --> 00:03:49.910
every single one of them.

00:03:51.910 --> 00:03:52.750
Thank you, Huaijin.

00:03:52.960 --> 00:03:54.840
If you like them, I...

00:03:55.120 --> 00:03:56.150
Sorry for the long wait.

00:03:56.800 --> 00:03:58.590
I wonder what matters bring you here.

00:03:59.910 --> 00:04:00.829
Long time no see.

00:04:01.000 --> 00:04:02.430
I came to visit you.

00:04:03.840 --> 00:04:04.680
(I'd like to see)

00:04:05.310 --> 00:04:06.910
(what tricks you have again.)

00:04:11.910 --> 00:04:12.750
Ruoli,

00:04:13.400 --> 00:04:14.860
you haven't been resting well lately.

00:04:15.150 --> 00:04:16.800
I have a fine blend of calming incense.

00:04:17.560 --> 00:04:18.953
I'll have someone deliver it to you,

00:04:19.270 --> 00:04:20.190
okay?

00:04:21.310 --> 00:04:22.150
Thank you.

00:04:29.040 --> 00:04:29.880
(What?)

00:04:30.240 --> 00:04:32.160
(Lu Huaijin admires her too?)

00:04:38.160 --> 00:04:39.000
Dear.

00:04:46.430 --> 00:04:47.270
What is it?

00:05:09.000 --> 00:05:10.920
We need to talk.

00:05:11.270 --> 00:05:12.110
Yanzhi,

00:05:12.270 --> 00:05:13.160
you're hurting her.

00:05:17.560 --> 00:05:18.800
Not your business.

00:05:33.270 --> 00:05:34.120
(Just as I thought,)

00:05:34.413 --> 00:05:36.126
(Lu Huaijin has feelings
for Jiang Ruoli.)

00:05:36.800 --> 00:05:37.720
(Jiang Ruoli,)

00:05:38.390 --> 00:05:39.376
(you don't deserve this.)

00:05:46.430 --> 00:05:47.270
Lady Wanyue,

00:05:47.499 --> 00:05:48.765
I must've made a fool of myself.

00:05:49.510 --> 00:05:50.350
What a pity.

00:05:50.630 --> 00:05:52.480
She doesn't feel the same way.

00:05:53.360 --> 00:05:54.630
With your status,

00:05:55.310 --> 00:05:56.716
why bring such shame upon yourself?

00:05:57.630 --> 00:05:58.600
You're right.

00:05:59.650 --> 00:06:00.756
Some things can't be forced.

00:06:01.480 --> 00:06:02.320
However,

00:06:03.040 --> 00:06:04.360
even if she isn't my wife,

00:06:05.160 --> 00:06:06.600
she's still the dearest family member

00:06:06.726 --> 00:06:07.846
I'd protect no matter what.

00:06:08.800 --> 00:06:09.750
This feeling in my heart

00:06:10.390 --> 00:06:11.600
will never change.

00:06:14.160 --> 00:06:15.413
Sorry. I can't stay any longer.

00:06:15.750 --> 00:06:16.590
Goodbye.

00:06:32.310 --> 00:06:33.310
You're hurting me.

00:06:33.720 --> 00:06:34.560
Jiang Ruoli,

00:06:35.430 --> 00:06:36.870
I know you had a past with him.

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:40.680
But you are my formal wife.

00:06:41.830 --> 00:06:43.310
I don't care what you two were before.

00:06:43.870 --> 00:06:45.120
Remember who you are.

00:06:45.560 --> 00:06:46.400
Stay away from him.

00:06:47.270 --> 00:06:48.160
Let me go first.

00:06:48.830 --> 00:06:49.670
Huo Linchuan,

00:06:49.950 --> 00:06:51.310
he's just a childhood friend.

00:06:52.160 --> 00:06:53.000
I...

00:06:53.000 --> 00:06:54.530
ظآزWhere shall I seekظآز

00:06:54.530 --> 00:06:57.320
ظآزThe traces of your past livesظآز

00:06:58.300 --> 00:07:02.900
ظآزI'd spend a lifetime's luck
just for youظآز

00:07:03.860 --> 00:07:08.730
ظآزGazing at your figure
for the rest of my lifeظآز

00:07:09.140 --> 00:07:14.210
ظآزUntil time grows us oldظآز

00:07:15.090 --> 00:07:19.780
ظآزDreams lift the night
where stars grow thinظآز

00:07:21.070 --> 00:07:22.040
You belong

00:07:23.750 --> 00:07:24.950
only to me.

00:07:26.170 --> 00:07:30.660
ظآزThe galaxy stirs;
destiny endlessly returnsظآز

00:07:31.060 --> 00:07:36.340
ظآزIf I could, let me guard you this timeظآز

00:07:36.560 --> 00:07:39.180
ظآزHow did this feeling beginظآز

00:07:39.400 --> 00:07:41.980
ظآزIn each trial, longing deepensظآز

00:07:42.230 --> 00:07:44.620
ظآزAcross vast lands, it still shinesظآز

00:07:44.810 --> 00:07:47.610
ظآزWhen the night fades,
the moon shines longerظآز

00:07:47.800 --> 00:07:50.160
ظآزA fleeting dream
shines through the rainظآز

00:07:50.520 --> 00:07:52.920
ظآزThrough three lifetimes,
we never partظآز

00:07:53.330 --> 00:07:58.780
ظآزA thousand years of snow
fall into your palmظآز

00:07:58.960 --> 00:08:01.470
ظآزHow does love fade awayظآز

00:08:01.740 --> 00:08:04.210
ظآزEach thought recalls the pastظآز

00:08:04.530 --> 00:08:07.090
ظآزLonging burns into a lasting acheظآز

00:08:07.560 --> 00:08:08.400
Huo Linchuan,

00:08:09.510 --> 00:08:10.350
I'm tired

00:08:11.680 --> 00:08:12.680
of suspicion,

00:08:13.310 --> 00:08:14.150
endless schemes,

00:08:15.830 --> 00:08:17.750
and the nightmares that never end.

00:08:18.390 --> 00:08:19.230
Then,

00:08:20.360 --> 00:08:21.360
what are we now,

00:08:22.680 --> 00:08:24.070
you and I?

00:08:25.160 --> 00:08:26.000
I want you

00:08:27.240 --> 00:08:28.430
to marry me.

00:08:29.720 --> 00:08:30.560
Alright.

00:08:39.000 --> 00:08:40.120
That kiss just now

00:08:41.000 --> 00:08:42.030
was not a deal,

00:08:42.750 --> 00:08:43.870
nor a momentary arrangement.

00:08:45.200 --> 00:08:46.040
Alright.

00:08:47.360 --> 00:08:48.510
From this moment on,

00:08:50.360 --> 00:08:52.080
whether it's life or death between us,

00:08:53.420 --> 00:08:54.960
there shall be no more secrets.

00:08:54.960 --> 00:08:59.670
ظآزGazing at your figure
for the rest of my lifeظآز

00:09:00.090 --> 00:09:04.940
ظآزUntil time grows us oldظآز

00:09:08.120 --> 00:09:08.960
Mr. Huo.

00:09:30.120 --> 00:09:31.640
ظآزThe dream shatteredظآز

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:33.680
ظآزLike illusion, yet trueظآز

00:09:33.680 --> 00:09:35.320
ظآزLike a restless soulظآز

00:09:36.200 --> 00:09:37.760
ظآزHow vagueظآز

00:09:38.160 --> 00:09:39.680
ظآزRain and blood, drifting wildظآز

00:09:39.680 --> 00:09:41.920
ظآزA blade of frost in dreamsظآز

00:09:42.720 --> 00:09:45.320
ظآزLove and hate entwinedظآز

00:09:45.800 --> 00:09:48.640
ظآزRise and fall, yet never fadeظآز

00:09:49.280 --> 00:09:54.040
ظآزHow can I turn the tides
of this fleeting lifeظآز

00:09:54.640 --> 00:09:56.160
ظآزWhen fate falls apartظآز

00:09:56.560 --> 00:10:00.120
ظآزMemories return,
carving tears upon my faceظآز

00:10:00.840 --> 00:10:02.400
ظآزYet I can't hold onظآز

00:10:02.800 --> 00:10:06.520
ظآزOnly warmth remains
where longing once burnedظآز

00:10:07.240 --> 00:10:10.080
ظآزLife after lifeظآز

00:10:10.560 --> 00:10:13.240
ظآزFated to meet, but never meant to beظآز

00:10:13.880 --> 00:10:17.960
ظآزStill, I refuse to bow or yieldظآز

00:10:18.040 --> 00:10:21.080
ظآزIn this life, love becomes my bladeظآز

00:10:21.240 --> 00:10:22.640
ظآزTo break free from reincarnationظآز

00:10:22.640 --> 00:10:25.760
ظآزAll past affairs tangled with regretظآز

00:10:25.840 --> 00:10:27.280
ظآزNow shatter apartظآز

00:10:27.400 --> 00:10:31.160
ظآزBy fate and karmic ties confinedظآز

00:10:31.880 --> 00:10:34.680
ظآزIs this fate or calamityظآز

00:10:34.960 --> 00:10:37.800
ظآزIs it life, death, or parting painظآز

00:10:38.120 --> 00:10:42.520
ظآزI ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heartظآز

00:10:42.760 --> 00:10:45.680
ظآزIn the next life, grant me one kissظآز

00:10:45.800 --> 00:10:50.240
ظآزTo kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gazeظآز

00:10:50.440 --> 00:10:56.160
ظآزFor once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never partظآز

00:10:56.600 --> 00:10:59.320
ظآزThis fleeting life feels but a dreamظآز

00:10:59.560 --> 00:11:02.280
ظآزSober or indulgeظآز

00:11:02.720 --> 00:11:08.720
ظآزI only wish to be with you,
with all my heartظآز